additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Dosage form: Tablet, film coated Quantity: 60 tablets Active ingredients per tablet: Glucosamine hydrochloride 750 mg Bovine sodium chondroitin sulfate (chondroitin) 200 mg Dimethyl Sulfone (MSM) 250 mg Manganese gluconate 8.8 mg - Equiv. manganese 1 mg Borax 8.8 mg - Equiv. boron 1 mg Derived from seafood.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Always read the label. Follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Contains crustacean products. Derived from seafood.

description: Nature's Way Joint Restore Triple Action contains glucosamine, plus chondroitin and dimethyl sulfone (MSM). This formulation can help support joint health, and helps build and maintain cartilage.
name: Glucosamine + Chondroitin + MSM
